column5: OUR GROUP WILL BE FISHING OUT OF THE FISHERIES CAMP JULY 7 - 13.WOULD APPRECIATE ANY CURRENT INFO ON SMALLIES, EYES AND NORTHERNS. THANKS IN ADVANCE.FISHED OUT OF LABELLES LAST YEAR AND OUT OF A HOUSEBOAT THE YEAR BEFORE (NORTH EAST END). HAD A GREAT TIME! THIS IS OUR FIRST TIME FISHING RED GUT.PATHFINDER
